<emphasis id="B96B5454FFC6DC6FFF6AFF2A164CFF0E" bold="true" box="[192,372,193,217]" pageId="18" pageNumber="17">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only in the 
<collectingCountry id="F308C8D6FFC6DC6FFDCFFF291428FF0D" box="[613,784,194,218]" name="United States of America" pageId="18" pageNumber="17">United States</collectingCountry>
