<collectingRegion id="49DB46A4FFC6DC6FFE83FE4916B5FE6D" box="[297,397,418,442]" country="United States of America" name="Arizona" pageId="18" pageNumber="17">Arizona</collectingRegion>
, where all of the known specimens were collected.
</paragraph>
